Pomowa, short for power mode watcher, can run programs when it detects your computer is waking from or going to sleep.

Thanks to Jonas Rask (http://www.jonasraskdesign.com) for the "Joost" icon archive where the Pomowa icon was retrieved.

Developed and maintained by Brian Hasden (http://www.brianhasden.com).

History of Changes:
0.1.0 - Initial Release